            "steps": [
                "Follow pain management protocols prescribed by your doctor.",
                "Discuss preventative medications if stones are recurrent."
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "Lifestyle",
            "steps": [
                "Increase fluid intake significantly (mostly water).",
                "Adjust diet based on stone type (e.g., limit sodium or oxalates)."
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "Escalation Awareness",
            "steps": [
